CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Healthcare Trust Inc is a Real estate investment trust in the United States. It invests in healthcare real estate, focusing on seniors housing properties and medical office buildings. The company also invests in facilities leased to hospitals, rehabilitation hospitals, long-term acute care centers, surgery centers, inpatient rehabilitation facilities, special medical and diagnostic service providers, laboratories, and research firms among others.
